## üé≠ **Animation & Spiritual Interaction Libraries**

### **AOS (Animate On Scroll)**
- **Library**: [AOS - Animate On Scroll](https://michalsnik.github.io/aos/)
- **Author**: Micha≈Ç Sajn√≥g
- **License**: MIT License
- **Version**: 2.3.1
- **Usage**: Reverent scroll animations, spiritual content revelation
```html
<link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.js"></script>
```
```javascript
AOS.init({
  duration: 1500,
  easing: 'ease-in-out-cubic',
  once: true,
  offset: 100,
  // Gentle, reverent animations
  anchorPlacement: 'top-bottom'
});
```

### **Particles.js**
- **Library**: [Particles.js](https://vincentgarreau.com/particles.js/)
- **Author**: Vincent Garreau
- **License**: MIT License
- **Usage**: Ethereal background effects, divine light particles
```javascript
particlesJS('divine-particles', {
  particles: {
    number: { value: 50 },
    color: { value: '#FFD700' },
    shape: { type: 'circle' },
    opacity: {
      value: 0.6,
      random: true,
      anim: {
        enable: true,
        speed: 1,
        opacity_min: 0.1
      }
    },
    size: {
      value: 3,
      random: true,
      anim: {
        enable: true,
        speed: 2,
        size_min: 0.1
      }
    },
    move: {
      enable: true,
      speed: 1,
      direction: 'top',
      out_mode: 'out'
    }
  }
});
```

