## üé® **CSS Techniques & Sacred Design Patterns**

### **Sacred Geometry CSS**
- **Golden Ratio Implementation**
  - Reference: [Golden Ratio in Design](https://www.canva.com/learn/what-is-golden-ratio/)
  - Usage: Harmonious proportions in spiritual layouts
```css
:root {
  --golden-ratio: 1.618;
  --sacred-unit: 1rem;
  --sacred-small: calc(var(--sacred-unit) / var(--golden-ratio));
  --sacred-medium: calc(var(--sacred-unit) * var(--golden-ratio));
  --sacred-large: calc(var(--sacred-medium) * var(--golden-ratio));
}

.blessing-card {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: calc(400px * var(--golden-ratio));
  padding: var(--sacred-medium);
  margin-bottom: var(--sacred-large);
  
  /* Sacred geometry proportions */
  aspect-ratio: var(--golden-ratio);
}

.mandala-container {
  width: 200px;
  height: 200px;
  position: relative;
  
  /* Perfect circle for sacred geometry */
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: radial-gradient(
    circle at center,
    var(--sacred-gold) 0%,
    var(--peaceful-blue) 50%,
    var(--divine-white) 100%
  );
}
```

