### **High Contrast Spiritual Themes**
- **Accessibility-First Color Schemes**
```css
/* High contrast theme for accessibility */
.theme-high-contrast {
  --primary: #000000;
  --secondary: #FFFFFF;
  --accent: #FFD700;
  --text: #000000;
  --background: #FFFFFF;
  --border: #000000;
  
  /* Ensure minimum 7:1 contrast ratio */
  --link-color: #0000EE;
  --visited-link: #551A8B;
  --focus-outline: #FF6600;
}

.theme-high-contrast .blessing-card {
  border: 2px solid var(--border);
  background: var(--background);
  color: var(--text);
}

.theme-high-contrast button:focus,
.theme-high-contrast a:focus {
  outline: 3px solid var(--focus-outline);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}

/* Reduced motion for accessibility */
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .spiritual-animation,
  .mandala-rotation,
  .breathing-animation {
    animation: none;
  }
  
  .aos-animate {
    transform: none !important;
    opacity: 1 !important;
  }
}

/* High contrast media query */
@media (prefers-contrast: high) {
  :root {
    --primary: #000000;
    --secondary: #FFFFFF;
    --accent: #FFD700;
    --text: #000000;
    --background: #FFFFFF;
  }
}
```

